<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ZOH LAW NUNG CH141</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa sinin thawng ka theih, Hal-le-lu-jah, Cu thawngtha cu nang kan
 thanh lai; A biathiang chungah a um Hal-le-lu-jah, Zoh law nung tuah ti
 bia thiang a si.

[C1]
   Maw unau, zoh law nung tuah, Jesuh zoh law na nung lai, A bia thiang
   chungah a um. Hal-le-lu-jah, Zoh law nung tuah ti bia thiang a si.

[V2]
 A dawtnak thawngtha ka ngei, Hal-le-lu-jah, Nangmah ca ah thanhmi
 thawngtha; Cunglei in thanhmi thawngtha Hal-le-lu-jah, Jesuh chimmi
 biatak cu ka hngalh.

[C2]
   Maw unau, zoh law nung tuah, Jesuh zoh law na nung lai, A bia thiang
   chungah a um. Hal-le-lu-jah, Zoh law nung tuah ti bia thiang a si.

[V3]
 Nunnak cu pek na si cang, Hal-le-lu-jah, Zungzal nunnak cu na ngei
 lai; Amah lawng kha va zoh tuah, Hal-le-lu-jah, Jesuh lawng khamh khotu
 asi.

[C3]
   Maw unau, zoh law nung tuah, Jesuh zoh law na nung lai, A bia thiang
   chungah a um. Hal-le-lu-jah, Zoh law nung tuah ti bia thiang a si.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>141</hymn_number>
</song>